|Related metaphor.Name=QUANTITY IS VERTICALITY
|Related metaphor.Description=more of something is usually good
}}
|Entailments={{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Well-being (feeling well physically and/or psychologically)
|Entailment.Source inference=Upward motion along or high point on a vertical scale
|Entailment.Type=scalar
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=WELL-BEING IS UP
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=Ill-being (feeling bad physically and/or psychologically)
|Entailment.Source inference=Downward motion along or low point on a vertical scale
|Entailment.Type=scalar
|Entailment.Entailed metaphors=ILL-BEING IS DOWN
}}
